00:24:41,599 --> 00:24:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, u prijevodu to bi bio jedan stabilni, nova stabilna valuta i ne znam ako je to zanimljivo mogu to.

211
00:24:49,839 --> 00:24:52,079
[SPEAKER_01] Da, recite, o čemu je zapravo riječ?

212
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:52,799
[SPEAKER_01] Stable coin.

213
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:56,640
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ovako, stable coin je stabilna valuta.

214
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] Što to znači?

